      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "The dynamic is rarely just one thing; it's usually a mix of loud, affectionate chaos and underlying, unspoken rules. Authority figures might be present, but they often express it through gentle prodding or sharp, witty banter rather than strict commands. Conversations can swing from deep, serious discussions about life to loud, humorous critiques of the day, all happening simultaneously. The real texture comes from the layered way people speak to each other—a mix of colloquialisms, inside jokes, and coded language.",
      "source": "target",
